<p>Unleash your vision with this heavyweight 240 GSM vest, built for the bold. The front features a striking “DRIP STUDIOS” print, paired with classic streetwear art and an embossed logo for a textured, standout finish. On the back, a powerful message—“CREATOR OF MY OWN REALITY”—sets the tone for self-expression and independence. Designed with a relaxed fit and premium cotton, this vest delivers all-day comfort with undeniable presence. Whether you’re on the grind or making a statement, this piece speaks loud. Streetwear isn’t just fashion—it’s a mindset. Own yours with DRIP STUDIOS.
</p>
<h4>Care Guide</h4><p>Machine wash the t-shirt inside out with like colors.
