Store the t-shirt in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.
</p>
<h4>Core Features</h4><p>T-shirts with 240 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.
Oversized fit for comfortable and versatile wear by both men and women.
Unisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.
Soft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.</p>
